291"
RESULTS,0.6198830409356725,"we change Œª in Figure 8. We can see when FA improves or performs similarly for a range of Œª. Here,
292"
RESULTS,0.6213450292397661,"we set p and f to satisfy the strong Byzantine resilience condition of Bulyan, i.e, p ‚â•4f + 3.
